Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,介绍我们国家的语言 法尔巴尼语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是 {\rSemanian\fnAvenirNextW1G-Demi\fs55}Dāshu·zanna
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用地球人的语言来说
